    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After Me</strong> first-person psychological thriller with elements of survival horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/a5a3f2f5a810a7dc95b522b2ed89138b.poster.avif?t=1729363742\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/a5a3f2f5a810a7dc95b522b2ed89138b.webm?t=1729363742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/a5a3f2f5a810a7dc95b522b2ed89138b.mp4?t=1729363742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Description:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character Tom is an artist, seeking for inspiration. He suffers from frequent migraines and decides to move from a noisy city to a quiet house in a countryside, which he has bought for a very nice price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the game you need to solve different puzzles and even shoot with a pistol. It will help you to explore the house and to find out what’s happening there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe the evil is closer than you think?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/2c937e79cf1dcd565dd02906d0b8146a.poster.avif?t=1729363742\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/2c937e79cf1dcd565dd02906d0b8146a.webm?t=1729363742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181850/extras/2c937e79cf1dcd565dd02906d0b8146a.mp4?t=1729363742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Peculiarities:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The plot is presented without the use of text</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-You will need to shoot with a pistol to complete some puzzles</p>",
